name: hikikomori
description: This project is about the tokenization of “Hikikomori”. It is a cultural phenomenon where one excludes themselves from society completely. Mainly, they stay home all day, every day. They can also have jobs, but have no interest in participating in the outside world. "pulling inward, being confined") are reclusive adolescents or adults who withdraw from social life, often seeking extreme degrees of isolation and confinement. The term refers to both the sociological phenomenon in general and the individuals belonging to this societal group.
